Boredom has forced most people to keep themselves entertained and at the same time show their hidden talents. Even Miss Universe Zozi Tunzi has shared her singing talent and it's evident that she loves to sing. Over the last the years she has posted several videos of herself singing several popular songs, including her own rendition of Amanda Black's Amazulu, which she got a stamp of approval from Amanda when she posted it on her Twitter page. This popular title track was written by Amanda Antony, Mnqobi Nxumalo and Christer KobediÂ . It was released in 2016 and it received a Song Of the Year nomination at the South African Music Awards.  